item.title: [PI]Private Access Code?[PI]
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

[quote=“NumberEleven, post:2, topic:399735”]go to clickingbuttons.java

and click ctrl + g

Then search 1546, and just delete the line / edit it.[/quote]

No, the error says nothing even close to that.

It means that instead of

public void doSomething() {
    // ...
}

The public is replaced with private. Meaning that you can’t call the method outside the class.
